Q1  -->  create a repeating linear gradient in CSS? 
code:------------------------- CSS file-------------------------------
 background-image:repeating-linear-gradient(40deg,red,yellow,green 45px);  /* after 45px it will repeat.*/
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------
 
Q2  -->  Add color overlay on image?   
code: -------------------------CSS file--------------------------------
*{
   margin:0;
   padding:0;
   box-sizing:border-box;
}
section{
    width:100%;
    height:100vh;
background-image:linear-gradient(      
        to right top,
        rgba(226, 126, 12, 0.5),
        rgba(29, 201, 81, 0.5),
        rgba(8,88,56,0.5),
        rgba(212, 61, 99, 0.5)
    ),
     url("https://images.pexels.com/photos/3888151/pexels-photo-3888151.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1");
     background-repeat:no-repeat;
     background-size:cover;
}
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ 
-------------------------------HTML file----------------------------------------------------
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Gradients</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <section></section>
</body>
</html>
